quran[10{c,v,t}:
23,18,aur aasman se hum ne theek hisaab ke mutabiq aik khaas miqdaar mein pani utaara aur is ko zameen meintehra diya hum ussay jis terhan chahain gayab kar satke hain
23,19,"phir is pani ke zareya se hum ne tumahray liye khajoor aur angoor ke baagh peda kar diye, tumahray liye un baghoon mein bohat se lazeez phal hain aur un se tum rozi haasil karte ho"
23,20,"aur woh darakht bhi hum ne peda kya jo tor sinaa se nikalta hai, tail bhi liye hue ugta hai aur khanay walon ke liye saalan bhi"
23,21,"aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumahray liye maweshion mein bhi aik sabaq hai un ke paiton mein jo kuch hai isi mein se aik cheez hum tumhe pilate hain, aur tumahray liye un mein bohat se dosray doosray faiday bhi hain"
23,22,unn ko tum khatay ho aur unn par aur kashtiyon par sawaar bhi kiye jatay ho
23,23,"hum ne Nooh ko is ki qoum ki taraf bheja is ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Allah ki bandagi karo, is ke siwa tumahray liye koi aur mabood nahi hai, kya tum drtay nahi ho? """
23,24,"is ki qoum ke jin sardaro ne maan-ne se inkaar kya woh kehnay lagey ke"" yeh shakhs kuch nahi hai magar aik bashar tum hi jaissa iss ki gharz yeh hai ke tum par bartari haasil kere Allah ko agar bhejna hota to farishtay bhejta yeh baat to hum ne kabhi apne baap dada ke waqton mein suni hi nahi ( ke bashar rasool ban kar aeye )"
23,25,"kuch nahi, bas is aadmi ko zara junoon la-haq ho gaya hai kuch muddat aur dekh lau ( shayad afaqa ho jaye ) """
23,26,"Nooh ne kaha"" parvar-digaar, un logon ne jo meri tkzib ki hai is par ab to hi meri madad farma """
23,27,"hum ne is par wahi ki ke"" hamari nigrani mein aur hamari wahi ke mutabiq kashti tayyar kar phir jab hamara hukum aa jaye aur tanoor ubal parre to har qisam ke janwaron mein se aik aik jora le kar is mein sawaar ho ja, aur apne ahal o Ayal ko bhi sath le siwaye unn ke jin ke khilaaf pehlay hi faisla ho chuka hai, aur zaalmon ke maamla mein mujh se kuch nah kehna, yeh ab ghark honay walay hain"
